            . About a quarter after nine o'clock at night, I went to the stall to get something; I locked it up again, and left it safe. I was going by at ten o'clock, and saw a light there. I found the staple had been wrenched off - I opened the door, and saw the prisoner with a bag, containing the articles stated in the indictment - He had put them into the bag; I secured him; I found a piece of iron on him.</p>
